responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "6AC343CF4CDD040ED7D9C2A7E08D45C4", "You know the rules, my deary. An offering to the pot and a fate I can reveal. But you have no precious bones to offer. Perhaps the skulls filled with insanity and gibbierish will do. The pot awaits.")
